BOS Framework Implementation License

This software implements the BOS (Business Operating System) Framework 
methodologies for solopreneur business excellence. The BOS Framework 
principles and methodologies are designed to be freely shared and 
implemented for individual entrepreneur success.

The BOS Framework emphasizes:
- Business Chassis optimization through systematic excellence
- Client Success Blueprint methodology for customer-centric operations
- Four-Engine Innovation Cycle for continuous business improvement
- Asset-driven operating model with AI augmentation
- Solopreneur advantage amplification through systematic frameworks

Contributors and users are encouraged to share improvements and 
adaptations that advance the mission of solopreneur business excellence 
while maintaining the core principles of systematic excellence, 
customer success, and exponential value delivery.